(8471, '_transient_wow_estore_plugins', 'a:19:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":28:{s:4:\"name\";s:41:\"Border Menu &#8211; sticky hamburger menu\";s:4:\"slug\";s:11:\"border-menu\";s:7:\"version\";s:3:\"3.0\";s:6:\"author\";s:49:\"<a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/\">Wow-Company</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:37:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/wpcalc\";s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"3.2\";s:6:\"tested\";s:3:\"5.3\";s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"5.3\";s:6:\"rating\";i:0;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:0;i:4;i:0;i:3;i:0;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:0;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:0;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:0;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:0;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:70;s:10:\"downloaded\";i:3019;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2019-10-31 4:02pm GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2017-03-16\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:41:\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/border-menu\";s:8:\"sections\";a:4:{s:11:\"description\";s:4131:\"<p>WordPress sticky menu plugin &#8216;Border Menu&#8217; with hamburger button for creating animated border menu. The Border Menu is the easy-to-use WordPress menu plugin for setting up the unfolding menu through the &#8220;hamburger menu icon&#8221;. The tool allows you to create a convenient and compact navigation bar on the site. It is used only when necessary and does not distract the attention of users</p>\n<h4>Demo</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/item-preview/border-menu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">DEMO</a></p>\n<h4>Main features</h4>\n<p>The Border Menu plugin will give recognition to the design of your site. The extension allows to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>create 1 menu;</li>\n<li>select 4 items for the main button;</li>\n<li>insert any links;</li>\n<li>display modal windows through the insertion of shortcodes; </li>\n<li>use more than 600+ Font awesome icons;</li>\n<li>customize the color of the menu buttons;</li>\n<li>and more&#8230;</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Can be used for</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>site navigation;</li>\n<li>additional menu;</li>\n<li>user panel;</li>\n<li>block of contacts and much more.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The Border Menu plugin is the convenient and simple tool for creating an unfolding menu on the border of the page. Navigation through the &#8220;hamburger icon&#8221; focuses the attention of users on the content of the resource. Free expansion will allow you to try a new approach in developing the structure of the site. Increase the conversion by reducing the number of distractions.</p>\n<h4>Pro version</h4>\n<p>Select the Pro-version of the plugin to increase the conversion of the site and gain access to more settings:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/item-preview/border-menu-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pro version demo</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>create an unlimited amount of menus;</li>\n<li>change the width of the unfolding panel;</li>\n<li>change the size buttons, icons, tooltips;</li>\n<li>set the indent and button margin;</li>\n<li>add tooltips to each menu item for more information;</li>\n<li>select the color and the backlight for the icons, the background and color of the tooltips, overlay and much more;</li>\n<li>use the built-in social share, the print button and the main user menu;</li>\n<li>change the display based on the user&#8217;s status;</li>\n<li>tie the menu to the specific page language;</li>\n<li>customize the display of navigation on individual pages and posts, use exceptions, IDs, categories, and much more;</li>\n<li>and more&#8230;</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/item/border-menu-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Buy Pro version</a></p>\n<h4>Compatibility with other popular plugins</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/modal-window/\">Modal Window</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-herd-effect/\">Wow Herd Effect</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-skype/\">Wow Skype Buttons</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-countdown/\">Wow Countdown</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/side-menu/\">Side Menu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/float-menu/\">Float Menu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/bubble-menu/\">Bubble Menu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/border-menu/\">Border Menu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/slide-menu/\">Slide Menu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/vertical-icon-menu/\">Vertical Icon Menu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-forms/\">Wow Forms</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/viral-signup/\">Viral Signup</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-forms/\">Wow Forms</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/viral-signup/\">Viral Signup</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/hover-effects/\">Hover Effects</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wow-icons/\">Wow Icons</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/social-subscriber/\">Social Subscriber</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Support</h4>\n<p>Search for answers and ask your questions at <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/border-menu\">support center</a></p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:794:\"<ul>\n<li>Installation option 1: Find and install this plugin in the <code>Plugins</code> -&gt; <code>Add new</code> section of your <code>wp-admin</code></li>\n<li>Installation option 2: Download the zip file, then upload the plugin via the wp-admin in the <code>Plugins</code> -&gt; <code>Add new</code> section. Or unzip the archive and upload the folder to the plugins directory <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> via ftp</li>\n<li>Press <code>Activate</code> when you have installed the plugin via dashboard or press <code>Activate</code> in the in the <code>Plugins</code> list </li>\n<li>Go to <code>Border Menu</code> section that will appear in your main menu on the left</li>\n<li>Click <code>Add new</code> to create your first menu</li>\n<li>Setup your menu</li>\n<li>Click Save</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:628:\"<h4>3.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li