se it for early access with limited invites or for other scarcity-based campaigns.</li>\n<li>Limited signup + Viral sharing mode: limited signup form followed by a prompt to share your specified link &amp; bring you the referrals!</li>\n<li>Maximum 50 signups (get pro to unlock unlimited signups)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Other features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Emails are added to a built-in email list.</li>\n<li>Users who complete the goal (bring the specified amount of referrals) move to a separate list, so that you can see which users to award</li>\n<li>Change Texts. Write your own texts for any part of the plugin, including the submit button&#8217;s text.</li>\n<li>Specify The Amount Of Needed Referrals</li>\n<li>Insert the link you want users to share. You can add also an #anchor to it (useful for long landing pages, when you want to direct users to a certain part). Or you can enable the &#8216;Lead directly to form&#8217; option and users will be taken to the form directly.</li>\n<li>Fraud protection by session tracking. One user cannot enter multiple emails.</li>\n<li>Built-in twitter &amp; facebook share buttons</li>\n<li>Custom facebook share text</li>\n<li>No annoying page reloads after submitting the email</li>\n<li>Create up to 2 forms</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Pro version</h4>\n<p>Achieve even better results with the PRO version.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Unlimited amount of forms</li>\n<li>Unlimited email list to run serious campaigns</li>\n<li>Styling options</li>\n<li>Integration with services of emailing: MailChimp, Getresponse</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://wow-demo.com/wow-viral-signups-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pro version demo</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/en/wow-viral-signups-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Buy Pro version</a></p>\n<h4>Use with our other popular plugins to maximize your results</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Wow Modal Windows &#8211; create popups &amp; flyouts <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-modal-windows/\">Free version</a> | <a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/