Countdowns &#8211; easily create any countdowns, counters and timers\";s:4:\"slug\";s:13:\"mwp-countdown\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"3.1.1\";s:6:\"author\";s:84:\"<a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/author/admin/?author_downloads=true\">Wow-Company</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:37:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/wpcalc\";s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"4.3\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"5.2.4\";s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"5.3\";s:6:\"rating\";d:54;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:3;i:4;i:0;i:3;i:0;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:4;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:7;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:1;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:0;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:1000;s:10:\"downloaded\";i:15096;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2019-04-29 6:09am GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2016-08-08\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:44:\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-countdown/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:4:{s:11:\"description\";s:4972:\"<p>WordPress countdown plugin &#8216;Wow Countdowns&#8217; helps to create limited-time and limited-amount countdowns. Increase conversion by limiting your offer with an amount or time-based countdown. You can have the timers start over on page refresh or you can enable session tracking and the timer will not refresh.</p>\n<h4>Demo</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/item-preview/wow-countdowns/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wow Countdowns demo</a></p>\n<h4>Main features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Setup limited-time &amp; limited-amount offers</li>\n<li>Create scarcity effect with limited amount</li>\n<li>Create urgency effect with limited time</li>\n<li>Create a countdown for a certain time</li>\n<li>Create a countdown for a certain time, with user tracking (countdown will not start over on page refresh)</li>\n<li>Create a countdown with a certain amount</li>\n<li>Create a countdown with a certain amount, with user tracking (countdown will not start over on page refresh)</li>\n<li>Create a countdown to a certain date</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Other features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Show or hide days, hours, minutes and seconds</li>\n<li>Show or hide titles: &#8216;Days&#8217;, &#8216;Hours&#8217;, &#8216;Minutes&#8217;, &#8216;Seconds&#8217;</li>\n<li>Enter your own titles for &#8216;Days&#8217;, &#8216;Hours&#8217;, &#8216;Minutes&#8217;, &#8216;Seconds&#8217;. You can insert words in an other language, for example.</li>\n<li>Choose the delimiter type ( 00:00 , 00.00 , 00-00 , 00/00 , 00|00 )</li>\n<li>Choose the increment interval for the amount-based countdowns. For example, set it to tick every 3 seconds, 1 second or a fraction of a second. It&#8217;s up to you.</li>\n<li>Specify the increment amount for the amount-based countdowns. Have it tick one by one, or tens by tens, for example.</li>\n<li>Count up or down (for the amount-based countdowns)</li>\n<li>Specify a starting amount and an ending amount (for the amount-based countdowns)</li>\n<li>Style countdowns with regular wordpress editor or via CSS. Just style the container in which you paste the shortcode.</li>\n<li>Select the amount of days to reset the countdowns for a certain user. If you use session tracking, you can set when the countdowns will start over.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Pro version</h4>\n<p>Achieve even better results with the Pro version:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Unlimited amount of countdowns</li>\n<li>Powerful triggers &#8211; show or hide your content, your offers, depending on the countdown (Unique feature)</li>\n<li>Enable randomizer to create super realistic, convincing countdowns (Unique feature)</li>\n<li>Powerful styling</li>\n<li>Show counter depending on language (allows creating multi-language)</li>\n<li>Show counter depending on user (for all users, only for logged-in users, only for not logged-in users)</li>\n<li>And more&#8230;</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/item-preview/wow-countdown-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pro version demo</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/item/wow-countdowns-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Buy Pro version</a></p>\n<h4>Use with our other popular plugins to maximize your results</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Wow Modal Windows &#8211; create popups &amp; flyouts <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-modal-windows/\">Free version</a> | <a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/item/wow-modal-windows-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pro version</a></li>\n<li>Wow Side Menus &#8211; add fixed side buttons to your website &amp; lead users where you want (Unique plugin) <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-side-menu/\">Free version</a> | <a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/item/wow-side-menus-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pro version</a></li>\n<li>Wow Forms &#8211; create simple forms <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-forms/\">Free version</a> | <a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/item/wow-forms-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pro version</a></li>\n<li>Wow Herd Effects &#8211; create a queue effect on your website (Unique plugin) <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-herd-effect/\">Free version</a> | <a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/item/wow-herd-effects-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pro version</a></li>\n<li>Wow Viral Signups &#8211; run basic or limited optin campaigns, with viral sharing (Unique plugin) <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-viral-signup/\">Free version</a> | <a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/item/wow-viral-signups-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pro version</a></li>\n<li>Wow Skype Buttons &#8211; add a skype button to your website <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-skype/\">Free version</a> | <a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/item/wow-skype-buttons-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pro version</a></li>\n<li>Wow Marketing-WP Suite &#8211; all of the above plugins in a single ultimate marketing plugin <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/marketing-wp/\">Free version</a> | <a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/item/marketing-package/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pro version</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Support</h4>\n<p>Search for answers and ask your questions at <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/mwp-countdown\">support center</a></p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:1262:\"<ul>\n<li>Installation option 1: Find and install this plugin in the <code>Plugins</code> -&gt; <code>Add new</code> section of your <code>wp-admin</code></li>\n<li>Installation option 2: Download the zip file, then upload the plugin via the wp-admin in the <code>Plugins</code> -&gt; <code>Add new</code> section. Or unzip the archive and upload the folder to the plugins directory <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> via ftp</li>\n<li>Press <code>Activate</code> when you have installed the plugin via dashboard or press <code>Activate</code> in the in the <code>Plugins</code> list </li>\n<li>Go to <code>Wow Countdowns</code> section that will appear in your main menu on the left</li>\n<li>Click <code>Add new</code> to create your first countdown</li>\n<li>Setup your countdown</li>\n<li>Click Save</li>\n<li>Copy and paste the shortcode, such as [Wow-Countdowns id=1] to where you want the countdown to appear. </li>\n<li>If you want it to appear everywhere on your site, you can insert it for example in your <code>header.php</code>, like this: <code>&lt;?php echo do_shortcode(\'[Wow-Countdowns id=1]\');?&gt;</code></li>\n<li>If you want to insert the shortcode into a widget, use <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/shortcode-widget/\">this plugin</a></li>\n</ul>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:584:\"<h4>3.1.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: minor bugs</li>\n<li>Fixed: main class</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>3.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: minor bugs</li>\n<li>Added: Support page</li>\n<li>Added: Discount page</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>3.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Number font size, Delimiter font size, Title font size </li>\n<li>Added: Create 3 counter</li>\n<li>Changed: Admin style</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Verifying access to the folder &#8216;asset&#8217;.</li>\n<li>Fix: Optimized code.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed code</li>\n<li>Change style</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:1933:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/mwp-countdown/trunk/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=2