press.org/plugins/wow-icons/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:5:{s:11:\"description\";s:3296:\"<p>This plugin helps to display icons into post, page or menu item. Select any icon of 8 fonts and customize the appearance: change color, size, align etc.<br />\nYou can also select the icon and add it to the menu item, thus making menu more attractive.</p>\n<h4>Main features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>8 Great icon fonts </li>\n<li>More than 2500 icons</li>\n<li>Insert icons in post, page or menu</li>\n<li>Customize color, size, align</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Demo</h4>\n<p><a href=\"http://wow-estore.com/item-preview/wow-icons/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Demo</a></p>\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe class=\'youtube-player\' type=\'text/html\' width=\'640\' height=\'360\' src=\'https://www.youtube.com/embed/aYFgKMSgta4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent\' allowfullscreen=\'true\' style=\'border:0;\'></iframe></span>\n<h4>ADDITIONAL OPTIONS IN PRO VERSION</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/item-preview/wow-icons-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Demo Pro version</a></p>\n<p>Achieve even better results with the PRO version:</p>\n<pre>\n* Link on icon\n* Background Shape\n* Background Color\n* Animation\n* Icon title\n* Placing icon after the menu item\n* Icon color in the menu item\n* And more...\n</pre>\n<p><a href=\"https://wow-estore.com/en/wow-icons-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\">GET PRO VERSION</a></p>\n<h4>Available Icon Fonts</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Font Awesome ( fontawesome ) </li>\n<li>Fontello </li>\n<li>IcoMoon</li>\n<li>Open Iconic</li>\n<li>WordPress Dashicons</li>\n<li>Google Material Fonts</li>\n<li>JustVector Social Icons</li>\n<li>Payment Fonts</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>USE WITH OUR OTHER POPULAR PLUGINS TO MAXIMIZE YOUR RESULTS</h4>\n<p>Marketing tools</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/modal-window/\">Modal Window</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-herd-effect/\">Wow Herd Effect</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-skype/\">Wow Skype Buttons</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-countdown/\">Wow Countdown</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>For creating Menu:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/side-menu/\">Side Menu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/float-menu/\">Float Menu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/bubble-menu/\">Bubble Menu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/border-menu/\">Border Menu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/slide-menu/\">Slide Menu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/vertical-icon-menu/\">Vertical Icon Menu</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>For creating Forms:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mwp-forms/\">Wow Forms</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/viral-signup/\">Viral Signup</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>For Authorization:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wow-facebook-login/\">Wow Facebook Login</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wow-google-login/\">Wow Google Login</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Other:<br />\n* <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/hover-effects/\">Hover Effects</a><br />\n* <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wow-icons/\">Wow Icons</a></p>\n<h4>Support</h4>\n<p>Search for answers and ask your questions at <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/wow-icons\">support center</a></p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:599:\"<ul>\n<li>Installation option 1: Find and install this plugin in the <code>Plugins</code> -&gt; <code>Add new</code> section of your <code>wp-admin</code></li>\n<li>Installation option 2: Download the zip file, then upload the plugin through the wp-admin in the <code>Plugins</code> -&gt; <code>Add new</code> section. Or unzip the archive and upload the folder to the plugins directory <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> via ftp</li>\n<li>Press <code>Activate</code> when you have installed the plugin through dashboard or press <code>Activate</code> in the in the <code>Plugins</code> list</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:873:\"\n<h4>How to use Wow Icons Plugin?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Just edit your post / page and find icon generator button &#8220;Wow Icons&#8221; on the top left corner of post editor.<br />\nSelect the options of  icon  and click button &#8220;Insert Icon&#8221;.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>How to add an icon to menu?</h4>\n<p>\n<ul>\n<li>Go to page Wow Icons</li>\n<li>Select icon fonts for menu and click &#8220;Save&#8221;</li>\n<li>Generate class of icon</li>\n<li>Go to Appearance -&gt; Menus, select which menu item to which you want to add the icon, and add the icon class(es) under &#8216;CSS Classes (optional)&#8217;</li>\n<li>Save your menu</li>\n</ul>\n</p>\n<h4>Why don&#8217;t I see an option to add classes?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Under Appearance -&gt; Menus, click &#8216;Screen Options&#8217; (top right of screen) and make sure that &#8216;CSS Classes&#8217; is checked. If not &#8211; check it!</p>\n</p>\n\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:267:\"<h4>2.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Button in Post</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Typicons font</li>\n<li>Added: Support page</li>\n<li>Fixed: Admin style</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: minor bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:853:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/wow-icons/trunk/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=2078410\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/wow-icons/trunk/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=2078410\" alt=\"Insert shortcode in post, page\"></a><p>Insert shortcode in post, page</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/wow-icons/trunk/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=2078410\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/wow-icons/trunk/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=2078410\" alt=\"Setting icons for menu\"></a><p>Setting icons for menu</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/wow-icons/trunk/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=2078410\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/wow-icons/trunk/sc